CASE WHEN COALESCE(EXPIRY_DATE,'') <> ''  AND EXPIRY_DATE <> '20691231'  THEN to_date(TRIM(EXPIRY_DATE),'yyyy-MM-dd') 
WHEN EXPIRY_DATE = '20691231' THEN to_date('9999-12-31','yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
